@NODE "History" "History"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}History@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   @{B}0.1:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-02-10) (35143 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Made the GUI.
   · Added the menus.
   · Added support for Hexen, WarpHexen and VAxen.
   · You can choose the buffers for the drive Hexen lies on.
   · Added Hexen's, WarpHexen's and VAxen's parameters.
   · You can Load/Save the Hexen.cfg for Hexen, WarpHexen and VAxen.
   · Added some cheats.
   · Wrote the Guide.
@ENDNODE

